---
title: Carb Smart Marinara Meatballs with Mushrooms, Beef and Ciabatta
description: Craving tomato sauce without the carb hangover? This recipe delivers all the comfort of a rich sauce without the uncomfortable fullness after your meal!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1038_W20_CA_RV157498-1_Main_low-132e6175.jpg
